metadata.name: Rascal 001 (GroSkoutz by Grotke Collab)
metadata.description:
The "Rascals" Genesis Collection consists of 111 3D sculpted characters created by Yagamiii. 

Each Rascal is carefully sculpted and modeled on an iPad. An art focused, community-interactive project inspired by the cultures of film, art, anime, music, video games and much more. 

Find your inner Rascal in the collection, and explore expression in art.
